Description:
IT'S ALWAYS SUNNY IN FAIRWEATHER
"Looking for the perfect gift this Christmas? Buy a house."
You set yourself a target that you'd have bought a property in 2017. And here you are still looking.
With most agencies shutting-up shop and many buyers putting a pause on their search for a home, now is your chance to sneak in.
Not only that - this might be the last property in Officer to ever sell under $500,000. So be quick.
The property is brand new. Literally the builder finished last week. Investors who want a full seven years of depreciation I'm looking at you.
The house features:
- Three bedrooms, master with en-suite and walk-in robe;
- Open plan living and dining;
- Modern kitchen with loads of bench space;
- 9-foot ceilings;
- Floating laminex floorboards;
- Single car remote garage with internal access;
- Landscaped yards.
